# The @buf scope is served from the Buf Schema Registry's generated-SDK npm registry,
# not npmjs.com. The fivebits/pug module is public, so no auth token is needed — and
# adding an `_authToken` with an unset/empty value makes npm send a bad bearer token,
# which the registry rejects with 401. Leave it out.
@buf:registry=https://buf.build/gen/npm/v1/
